DIR STRUCTURE
----------------
.
|-- README -> this readme file
|-- ant -> ant related files, build.xml and maybe property file
|   `-- build.xml
|-- build -> files generated during compile, include classes and lib etc.
|-- config -> config files that will go into WEB-INF/classes
|-- dist -> distributables, war, jar
|-- etc -> web config files, web.xml, sun-application.xml etc.
|   `-- web.xml
|-- lib -> libraries
|-- src -> source code
`-- web -> web contents, html, jsp, etc.

